manasella neene is a 2002 kannada romance film directed by mugur sundar , a popular choreographer marking his debut in film direction .   the film stars nagendra prasad and gayathri raguram in the lead roles with prabhudeva and ananth nag in other pivotal roles .   the film is remake of the 2001 telugu film manasantha nuvve starring uday kiran and reemma sen. it was also remade in hindi as jeena sirf merre liye and in tamil as thithikudhe .